            . I had a chair belonging to me On Tuesday evening last, I left it in <placeName id="t18150621-23-crimeloc129">Tothill-court, South Audley-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18150621-23-crimeloc129" type="placeName" value="Tothill-court, South Audley-street"></interp>
