                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150621-23-off127 t18150621-23-crimeloc129"></join>; between the hours of eleven and twelve; the glass was safe then. The next morning, I missed one of the glasses, it was a window with two glasses in it; each cost three shillings and three pence. I saw it the next day, in the hands of a man whom I dont know.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150621-23-person241">
                  JOHN 
                  TIMBRELL
